- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper presents complexity results for various optimization problems. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the paper deals with combinatorial optimization problems. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a new complexity model for search algorithms. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper presents lower bounds on the number of function evaluations needed for optimization problems.
